    <updated>2021-06-02T13:00:30.097Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Repository mirroring allows for mirroring of repositories to and from external sources.<br><a id="more"></a></p><p><strong>参考资料</strong></p><ul><li>同步时间问题</li></ul><p><a href="https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/user/project/repository/repository_mirroring.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Repository mirroring</strong></a><br><a href="https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/237891" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Improve CI for external repo with configurable maximum mirroring frequency</a><br><a href="https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/12758" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Repository pull mirror scheduling design</a><br><a href="https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/gl-infra/scalability/-/issues/78#note_262385767" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reduce rate of RepositoryUpdateMirrorWorker jobs</a><br><a href="https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/118753" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Application limits for pull mirror API</a><br><a href="https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/blob/master/ee/lib/gitlab/mirror.rb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MIN_DELAY = 30.minutes</a><br><a href="https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/5258" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dynamically determine mirror update interval based on total number of mirrors, average update time, and available concurrency</a><br><a href="https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/administration/instance_limits.html#number-of-webhooks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitLab application limits</a></p><ul><li>其他</li></ul><p><a href="https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/ci/docker/using_docker_build.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Building Docker images with GitLab CI/CD</a></p><p><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1624837" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitLab Runner安装注册配置管理</a><br><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1530690" target="_blank" rel="noopener">如何做Git项目的持续集成</a><br><a href="https://www.upyun.com/tech/article/245/%E5%BD%93%E8%B0%88%E5%88%B0%20GitLab%20CI%20%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E8%AF%A5%E8%81%8A%E4%BA%9B%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%8A%E7%AF%87%EF%BC%89.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">(17年的文章，有点旧，但是技术细节还不错)当谈到 GitLab CI 的时候，我们该聊些什么（上篇）</a><br><a href="https://www.upyun.com/tech/article/246/%E5%BD%93%E8%B0%88%E5%88%B0%20GitLab%20CI%20%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E9%83%BD%E8%AF%A5%E8%81%8A%E4%BA%9B%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%8B%E7%AF%87%EF%BC%89.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">当谈到 GitLab CI 的时候，我们都该聊些什么（下篇）</a><br><a href="https://www.jqhtml.com/50142.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">基于镜像部署的Gitlab-CI/CD实践和坑位指南</a><br><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/jimaojin/p/12611584.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">docker运行gitlab runner且指定shell executor</a><br><a href="https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab-runner/-/blob/master/docs/configuration/advanced-configuration.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gitlab-runner docs configuration advanced-configuration</a><br><a href="https://docs.gitlab.com/runner/executors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Executors</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/libertine1993/article/details/80651552" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Docker 从容器中拷贝文件到宿主机中</a><br><a href="https://jingsam.github.io/2018/10/16/host-in-docker.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Docker容器访问宿主机网络</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/u010502101/article/details/89067757" target="_blank" rel="noopener">解决unable to locate package net-tools</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/q_Catherine/article/details/90741613" target="_blank" rel="noopener">修改gitlab默认端口</a><br><a href="https://zj-git-guide.readthedocs.io/zh_CN/latest/platform/GitLab%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B48080%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitLab导致8080端口冲突</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/wangyy130/article/details/85633303" target="_blank" rel="noopener">linux安装gitlab并修改gitlab默认端口号</a><br><a href="https://yeasy.gitbook.io/docker_practice/container/attach_exec" target="_blank" rel="noopener">docker从入门到实践</a><br><a href="https://blog.mayershi.me/2019/12/23/crack-gitlab-ee-licence/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gitlab-ee 企业版自签许可证license</a><br><a href="https://blog.starudream.cn/2020/01/19/6-crack-gitlab/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">生成 GitLab EE 许可证</a><br><a href="https://www.bookstack.cn/read/gitlab-doc-zh/docs-226.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gitlab 中文文档</a><br><a href="https://www.coder.work/article/6562560" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mirror确实可以工作，但是速度很慢</a><br><a href="https://about.gitlab.com/releases/2018/03/22/gitlab-10-6-released/#gitlab-cicd-for-external-repos" target="_blank" rel="noopener">External CI/CD configuration in Starter and Bronze</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/825dad1266cf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">配置 GitLab Runners</a><br><a href="https://bbs.aqzt.com/thread-621-1-1.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gitlab-ci-multi-runner和GitLab Runner区别</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/2b43151fb92e" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitLab-CI与GitLab-Runner</a><br><a href="https://docs.gitlab.com/runner/install/docker.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在容器中运行GitLab Runner</a><br><a href="https://juejin.im/post/6844904152955355149" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Docker安装Gitlab、Gitlab-Runner并实现项目CICD</a><br><a href="https://forge.etsi.org/rep/help/workflow/repository_mirroring.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Repository mirroring</a></p><p><a href="https://meigit.readthedocs.io/en/latest/gitlab_ci_.gitlab-ci.yml_detail.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitLab CI流水线配置文件.gitlab-ci.yml详解</a></p><ul><li>issue</li></ul><p><a href="https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab-foss/-/issues/57038" target="_blank" rel="noopener">reset_token_url: reset_registration_token_admin_application_settings_path</a><br><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/54216933/internal-server-error-500-while-accessing-gitlab-admin-runners" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Internal Server Error 500 while accessing $GITLAB/admin/runners</a></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/ouyang_peng/article/details/84066417" target="_blank" rel="noopener"></a></p><p><img src="http://static.zhyjor.com/wexin.png" alt></p>]]></content>
    
